========================================================
Along with this project the following files are attached
========================================================
1) Source files : PixelSum.cpp, PixelSum.h, Main.cpp, Common.h
2) PixelSumGPU.cpp : A Sample GPU implementation. Please donot compile
3) Answers to the essay questions

=====================
How to install.
=====================
1) Download the varjo-assignment-Sriram.zip and unzip.
2) cd varjo-assignment-Sriram/
3) mkdir build
4) cd build
5) cmake ..
6) make

=====================
How to run
=====================
1) cd build/
2) ./PixelSum